# Chat Plugin Contract Templates

## Intent
Provide enforceable templates for plugin command contracts, permission policies, and audit events.

## Required Template Set
- [chat-plugin-command-schema-template.mdc](chat-plugin-command-schema-template.mdc)
- [chat-plugin-permissions-schema-template.mdc](chat-plugin-permissions-schema-template.mdc)
- [chat-plugin-audit-schema-template.mdc](chat-plugin-audit-schema-template.mdc)

## Mandatory Usage
- Every plugin must implement all three templates before release.
- Contract versions must be explicit and backward compatibility documented.
- Contract validation must run in CI before merge.

## Release Blockers
- Missing template implementation for any plugin.
- Missing contract versioning or migration notes.